257
00:17:03.316 --> 00:17:07.176
signaling and also a more robust suppression of MYC

258
00:17:07.237 --> 00:17:07.856
expression.

259
00:17:08.916 --> 00:17:12.656
Extending this to a syngeneic model, KPC model, we see

