00:17:16.616 --> 00:17:20.576
not show much activity. Here you can see the activity of the RAS

262
00:17:20.596 --> 00:17:24.017
inhibitor. And then in combination, what you can see is nice

263
00:17:24.136 --> 00:17:28.056
regression. So this is in a syngeneic model, so we were able

264
00:17:28.096 --> 00:17:31.746
to ask questions about the impact of this combination on the

265
00:17:31.776 --> 00:17:35.016
immune cell population, and this is a summary of what we found.

