00:17:35.656 --> 00:17:39.336
We found that whereas RAS stimulated a T cell response,

267
00:17:39.876 --> 00:17:41.076
AXL inhibitor did not

268
00:17:42.236 --> 00:17:45.216
cause such a significant impact on T cells.

269
00:17:45.736 --> 00:17:49.126
But what we see here is that the AXL

