290
00:18:54.208 --> 00:18:56.888
And the other thing that we then looked at was whether there would be

291
00:18:56.928 --> 00:19:00.747
cross-resistance when cells became resistant to a RAS inhibitor.

292
00:19:01.368 --> 00:19:05.128
And what you can see here is that we established

293
00:19:05.208 --> 00:19:09.128
cells that were resistant to RAS inhibitor, and they were

294
00:19:09.168 --> 00:19:11.767
then cross-resistant to other RAS inhibitors.

295
00:19:12.648 --> 00:19:15.628
But then they remained very sensitive to

296
00:19:15.928 --> 00:19:16.988
ONC201.

297
00:19:18.588 --> 00:19:22.408
So, moving on to the last combination, looking

298
00:19:22.508 --> 00:19:23.948
at glutamine metabolism.

299
00:19:25.128 --> 00:19:28.768
So this one also, we will have a short talk

300
00:19:29.168 --> 00:19:32.958
in a session tomorrow by Wen Chang, a post-doc in the

301
00:19:33.028 --> 00:19:35.228
group, who will talk more about this in detail.

302
00:19:35.888 --> 00:19:39.468
So I'll just highlight a few of the observations that he made.

303
00:19:40.548 --> 00:19:44.028
So once again, we looked at existing

304
00:19:44.108 --> 00:19:48.008
KEAP1-NRF2 gene signatures, and we found

305
00:19:48.068 --> 00:19:51.908
that they were lacking. And as a consequence, we generated

306
00:19:51.968 --> 00:19:54.968
our own KEAP2 loss-driven

307
00:19:55.148 --> 00:19:57.608
signature in pancreatic cancer cells.

308
00:19:57.648 --> 00:19:59.528
And this is the signature that we generated.

309
00:20:00.088 --> 00:20:03.748
You can see here our comparison with existing signatures below here,

310
00:20:04.238 --> 00:20:08.088
and you can see that there's a fairly limited overlap between existing

311
00:20:08.148 --> 00:20:08.768
signatures.

312
00:20:09.908 --> 00:20:13.608
So then we compared the KEAP1

313
00:20:13.688 --> 00:20:15.408
loss generated

314
00:20:16.408 --> 00:20:19.608
gene transcription signature, and we asked whether there's any

315
00:20:19.648 --> 00:20:23.568
relationship between these genes and the previous

316
00:20:23.648 --> 00:20:27.368
gene transcriptomes of RAS, MYC,

317
00:20:27.868 --> 00:20:31.648
and TED. And so I previously told you that with RAS,

