00:20:31.988 --> 00:20:35.688
MYC, and TED, we saw a significant overlap of genes here.

319
00:20:36.368 --> 00:20:40.128
In contrast, KEAP1 loss and NRF2

320
00:20:40.188 --> 00:20:43.268
