340
00:21:53.888 --> 00:21:57.568
So in closing, what I'd like to emphasize is that while a

341
00:21:57.668 --> 00:22:01.488
lot of the combinations that are being evaluated are

342
00:22:01.628 --> 00:22:05.518
within the RAS signaling network, which makes sense

343
00:22:05.608 --> 00:22:08.828
because a lot of the resistance mechanisms have been identified there,

