348
00:22:25.048 --> 00:22:28.868
even if cells are resistant to a RAS

349
00:22:28.888 --> 00:22:29.328
inhibitor.

350
00:22:30.448 --> 00:22:34.378
So I'll stop there and acknowledge members of the group that have been involved in

351
00:22:34.408 --> 00:22:35.048
these studies.

